            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">Iuliae Augustae</supplied> Caelesti deae <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">matri Imperato</supplied>ris Caesaris <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aurelii Anton</supplied>ini Pii Felicis <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Augusti Parth</supplied>ici maximi <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">Britannici maxi</supplied>mi Germanici <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">maximi itemqu</supplied>e senatus patri<lb break="no" n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">ae et castror</supplied>um in honorem <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">legionis XXII A</supplied>ntoninianae <expan><abbr>Pr</abbr><ex>imigeniae</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></supplied>us Quirina An<lb break="no" n="10"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>iana <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Stein heute etwas weiter beschädigt. (B): Z. 6: Ésperandieu: (maximi, matr)e senatus...; Selzer: (maximi et matr)e senatus... Z. 6/7: Selzer: patri/(ae item castror)um... Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
